&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication and customer relation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding problem-solving and time management skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be an adept driver and always abide by all traffic rules&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional appearance, punctuality, and a positive attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professionalism, patience, and a process-driven approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work occasional evening and weekend shifts&lt;/li&gt;
