&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Feature Requests &amp;amp; Strategy Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage retail feature requests and maintain retail dossiers, data, and strategies. Present internally on relationship status and strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Organize and lead cross-functional retail stakeholder meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Retailer Engagement:&lt;/strong&gt; Track each retailer’s engagement across Nabis offerings, such as shelf space, marketplace, and inventory tool adoption

