&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employee engagement and culture. &lt;/strong&gt;You drive engagement through existing programs and develop new gamification initiatives designed to improve bi-annual employee engagement scores. You think creatively about how to keep a distributed, multi-site workforce connected and motivated.&lt;/p&gt;
